official_title: WIC-Based Intervention to Promote Healthy Eating Among Low-Income Mothers
inclusion_criteria:
* English- or Spanish-speaking
* Farmers' Market Nutrition Program (FMNP) voucher recipient or caregiver of a child FMNP voucher recipient
* Not less than 3 months from expected delivery date (pregnant women)
* Eligible to receive WIC benefits for 6 months after study entry
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
Must have maximum age of 99 Years
exclusion_criteria: ‚óè Restrictions of food intake (has food allergies or foods that cannot be eaten)
